---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Pricing — Gripmode"
metaDesc: "Simple, transparent pricing for martial arts school management. Plans from $19/mo. 7-day free trial, no credit card required."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
  - { name: "Pricing", url: "/pricing/" }
---

{% block extraHead %}
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#ffffff;--bg-soft:#f7f8fa;--text:#0f1115;--muted:#5f6672;--line:#e5e7eb;--black:#111315;--radius:16px;--dark-bg:#0f1114;
  }
  section{padding:88px 0}
  .pricing-hero{padding:96px 0 48px;text-align:center;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto}
  .pricing-hero .eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:#f4f4f5;border:1px solid var(--line);font-size:.83rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:24px}
  .sub{font-size:1.14rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:60ch;margin:0 auto}
  .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;padding:13px 18px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid transparent;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer}
  .btn-dark{background:var(--black);color:#fff}.btn-dark:hover{opacity:.92}
  .btn-light{background:#fff;color:#111;border-color:var(--line)}
  .pricing-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px;margin-top:48px}
  .card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:28px}
  .price{font-family:"Space Grotesk";font-size:2.4rem;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:8px 0}
  .price small{font-size:.95rem;color:var(--muted);font-family:"Plus Jakarta Sans"}
  .recommended{border:2px solid #111;box-shadow:0 18px 40px #0000000d;transform:translateY(-6px)}
  .list{padding-left:18px;margin:14px 0 0}
  .list li{margin:10px 0;color:#222;font-size:.95rem}
  .plan-desc{color:var(--muted);font-size:.95rem;min-height:44px}

  .comparison-section{padding:88px 0}
  .comparison-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-top:32px}
  .comparison-table th,.comparison-table td{padding:14px 16px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);font-size:.95rem}
  .comparison-table thead th{font-family:"Space Grotesk",sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;background:var(--bg-soft);position:sticky;top:0}
  .comparison-table thead th:first-child{border-radius:12px 0 0 0}
  .comparison-table thead th:last-child{border-radius:0 12px 0 0}
  .comparison-table tbody td{color:var(--muted)}
  .comparison-table tbody td:first-child{color:var(--text);font-weight:600}
  .comparison-table .check{color:var(--text);font-weight:700}
  .comparison-table .dash{color:var(--line)}

  .faq{display:grid;gap:12px;margin-top:32px}
  details{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 16px;background:#fff}
  summary{font-weight:700;cursor:pointer}

  @media (max-width:980px){
    section{padding:66px 0}
    .pricing-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .recommended{transform:none}
    .comparison-section{overflow-x:auto}
    .comparison-table{min-width:600px}
  }
</style>
{% endblock %}

<div class="gm-container">
  <section class="pricing-hero">
    <span class="eyebrow"><i data-lucide="tag" style="width:16px;height:16px"></i> No hidden fees</span>
    <h1>Simple, Transparent Pricing</h1>
    <p class="sub">Start with a 7-day free trial. No credit card required. Cancel anytime.</p>
  </section>

  <section style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Starter</h3>
        <div class="price">$19 <small>/month</small></div>
        <p class="plan-desc">For early-stage schools up to 150 members. Get the essentials to run a clean operation.</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Up to 150 members</li>
          <li>1 location</li>
          <li>Core operations dashboard</li>
          <li>Basic retention alerts</li>
          <li>Team management</li>
          <li>Basic scheduling</li>
          <li>Attendance tracking</li>
          <li>Email support</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-light" href="#trial" style="margin-top:18px;width:100%">Start Free Trial</a>
      </article>
      <article class="card recommended">
        <div style="background:var(--black);color:#fff;display:inline-block;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:999px;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px">MOST POPULAR</div>
        <h3>Growth</h3>
        <div class="price">$39 <small>/month</small></div>
        <p class="plan-desc">For established schools ready to scale. Full operational toolkit with advanced features.</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Up to 500 members</li>
          <li>Up to 2 locations</li>
          <li>Everything in Starter</li>
          <li>Full payroll system</li>
          <li>Advanced retention workflows</li>
          <li>Inventory management</li>
          <li>Full analytics dashboard</li>
          <li>CRM & lead management</li>
          <li>Advanced scheduling</li>
          <li>Priority support</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-dark" href="#trial" style="margin-top:18px;width:100%">Start Free Trial</a>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Multi-Location</h3>
        <div class="price">$79 <small>/month</small></div>
        <p class="plan-desc">For operators running 2+ schools. Centralized management and cross-location visibility.</p>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>Unlimited members</li>
          <li>Unlimited locations</li>
          <li>Everything in Growth</li>
          <li>Cross-location reporting</li>
          <li>Centralized controls</li>
          <li>Multi-location payroll</li>
          <li>Custom integrations</li>
          <li>Dedicated account manager</li>
          <li>Phone & email support</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-light" href="#trial" style="margin-top:18px;width:100%">Contact Sales</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="comparison-section">
    <h2>Feature Comparison</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:1.04rem">See exactly what's included in each plan.</p>
    <div style="overflow-x:auto">
      <table class="comparison-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="width:40%">Feature</th>
            <th style="width:20%">Starter</th>
            <th style="width:20%">Growth</th>
            <th style="width:20%">Multi-Location</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Members limit</td>
            <td>150</td>
            <td>500</td>
            <td>Unlimited</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Locations</td>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>2</td>
            <td>Unlimited</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Operations Dashboard</td>
            <td class="check">Basic</td>
            <td class="check">Full</td>
            <td class="check">Full + Multi-site</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Retention Alerts</td>
            <td class="check">Basic</td>
            <td class="check">Advanced workflows</td>
            <td class="check">Advanced workflows</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Payroll</td>
            <td class="dash">&mdash;</td>
            <td class="check">Full system</td>
            <td class="check">Multi-location</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Inventory</td>
            <td class="dash">&mdash;</td>
            <td class="check">Full</td>
            <td class="check">Full</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Analytics</td>
            <td class="dash">&mdash;</td>
            <td class="check">Full dashboard</td>
            <td class="check">Cross-location</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Scheduling</td>
            <td class="check">Basic</td>
            <td class="check">Advanced</td>
            <td class="check">Advanced</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>CRM & Lead Management</td>
            <td class="dash">&mdash;</td>
            <td class="check">Full</td>
            <td class="check">Full</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Multi-location Reporting</td>
            <td class="dash">&mdash;</td>
            <td class="dash">&mdash;</td>
            <td class="check">Full</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Custom Integrations</td>
            <td class="dash">&mdash;</td>
            <td class="dash">&mdash;</td>
            <td class="check">Available</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Support Level</td>
            <td>Email</td>
            <td>Priority email</td>
            <td>Dedicated manager</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Pricing FAQ</h2>
    <div class="faq">
      <details>
        <summary>Is there a free trial?</summary>
        <p style="color:var(--muted)">Yes. Every plan includes a 7-day free trial. No credit card required to start. You can explore the full feature set of your chosen plan before committing.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I switch plans later?</summary>
        <p style="color:var(--muted)">Absolutely. You can upgrade or downgrade your plan at any time. Changes take effect at the start of your next billing cycle. No penalties or fees.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Are there any setup fees?</summary>
        <p style="color:var(--muted)">No. There are no setup fees, onboarding fees, or hidden charges. The monthly price is the total price.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What payment methods do you accept?</summary>
        <p style="color:var(--muted)">We accept all major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express). For Multi-Location plans, we can also accommodate invoicing and bank transfers.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What happens when I cancel?</summary>
        <p style="color:var(--muted)">You can cancel anytime from your account settings. Your access continues until the end of your current billing period. We don't charge cancellation fees, and your data is available for export for 30 days after cancellation.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Do you offer annual billing?</summary>
        <p style="color:var(--muted)">Not yet, but it's on our roadmap. When we launch annual billing, it will include a discount compared to monthly pricing.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What if I have more than 500 members on Growth?</summary>
        <p style="color:var(--muted)">If your school grows beyond 500 members, we recommend moving to the Multi-Location plan for unlimited capacity. Contact us and we'll help you transition seamlessly.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  {% include "cta-section.njk" %}
</div>
